# Summary File Standards and Requirements
tags: ["summaries", "standards", "documentation"]
appliesTo: ["GPT", "CursorAgent", "Ghost"]
enforce: true
priority: high

## Rules

All `.summary.md` files must contain:

- ✅ Patch ID (exact match to filename)
- 🔗 Backlink to patch: `patchName: [patch-name]`
- 📍 Roadmap phase reference
- 💬 At least one GPT or DEV status message
- 🧪 Explicit validation summary (PASS/FAIL)
- 🕒 Timestamp or UTC trace
- 📁 Final file write location (`.completed`, `.archive`, `.failed`)


